{"tid":1077801,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"拉莫斯出戰挪威被讚好好先生　祖舒亞京治：「未見過防守球員好似佢咁好人。」","createTime":"2019-03-25T23:54:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-26T05:03:24.000Z","uid":173208,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"661d7e4d7f9ff6604e4fdd21c610062ebc363847","tid":1077801,"uid":173208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-25T23:54:36.000Z","msg":"後防球員要守護球隊難免會與敵隊進攻球員拳腳交加，但有時候「硬朗」並不代表要「骯髒」，而西班牙中堅沙治奧拉莫斯(Sergio Ramos)就經常被人指責動作骯髒，但在上星期的西班牙主場對挪威的賽事中，挪威前鋒祖舒亞京治(Joshua King)指拉莫斯是一位好好先生，有別於外界對拉莫斯的評語。<br />\n<br />\n在歐國盃外圍賽F組賽事，西班牙主場以2-1險勝挪威，今場比賽出現兩個十二碼，分別由祖舒亞京治和拉莫斯射入，而賽後兩人更有出人意表的事情發生。賽後祖舒亞京治大讚拉莫斯的行為，他指：「雖然拉莫斯風評差劣，但我從未見過一個球員像他一樣好人。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/79edff56d71a43b0e7b8f509113ef6b8/tumblr_powx3hwa9u1wguykjo1_1280.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F79edff56d71a43b0e7b8f509113ef6b8%2Ftumblr_powx3hwa9u1wguykjo1_1280.jpg&h=d29b8d41&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e990b282b83c3617ab756c7e920e0d801ead8354","tid":1077801,"uid":15950,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯:你咁廢 洗鬼矛你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a260ce133006999a41b12c9aa5ea4704ecdb59a","tid":1077801,"uid":96823,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:14:45.000Z","msg":"條友死獌狗"},{"pid":"59ded1f6d1308ea277fb821af0b8275894fbebca","tid":1077801,"uid":34571,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:26:18.000Z","msg":"對老婆係既"},{"pid":"b360f842772d5eb2baed4205bc30c009fee8dff4","tid":1077801,"uid":86136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e990b282b83c3617ab756c7e920e0d801ead8354","tid":1077801,"uid":15950,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯:你咁廢 洗鬼矛你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:46:14.000Z","msg":"True"},{"pid":"6603c25dbd3fd3c7cbbe6245a23b98ad387920d7","tid":1077801,"uid":214972,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"睇返沙拿下場先啦嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05bfe9acd664d69dbc411d860ed9164efcea6f71","tid":1077801,"uid":216021,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e990b282b83c3617ab756c7e920e0d801ead8354","tid":1077801,"uid":15950,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T00:42:22.000Z","msg":"拉莫斯:你咁廢 洗鬼矛你咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:55:18.000Z","msg":"三個level<br />\n一. 唔駛犯規都足已應付<br />\n二. 要靠犯規去加強防守先有把握應付<br />\n三. 靠犯規都應付唔到"},{"pid":"ab5076d872af902b76596664725f5bd0c3affca2","tid":1077801,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"6603c25dbd3fd3c7cbbe6245a23b98ad387920d7","tid":1077801,"uid":214972,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T01:51:40.000Z","msg":"睇返沙拿下場先啦嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T05:03:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}